         VERSION=1.3.5
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:7729a8f4cdd59af21ad6f054542ad112b7adf79e4d20194184f66d1a628d2b851b8affe851b74942ff59d23b10e2be42897bed0969ecf33a6a4fb9f80e4b2080
